islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b910942b1395ce94a868d49a54aca06e64522cfa","tid":1822593,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:13:14.000Z","msg":"【全球8國15市聯手，1.19 天下制裁大遊行！】<br />\n<br />\n攬炒團隊 同各國組織將會喺1.19同步發起遊行集會，支援 「民間集會團隊」發起嘅 1.19 港島東行《天下制裁大遊行》！<br />\n<br />\n即使面對嚴寒飛雪、史無前例山火，英美澳加紐德比等國居民 經過一個月籌備，仍然繼續聯手捍衛香港。<br />\n<br />\n謹此 懇切呼籲各地港人陸續響應號召，舉辦、參加1.19天下制裁行動，逆流打返起個勢！<br />\n<br />\n已確認1.19名單：<br />\n1. 香港 - 香港島<br />\n2. 美國 - 波士頓、洛杉磯、華盛頓特區、三藩市<br />\n3. 德國 - 柏林<br />\n4. 英國 - 倫敦、格拉斯哥<br />\n5.  澳洲 - 布里斯本 、墨爾本、悉民<br />\n6. 紐西蘭 - 奧克蘭、基督城<br />\n7. 比利時 - 布魯塞爾<br />\n8. 加拿大 - 溫哥華<br />\n<br />\n至於各地詳情，請留意 &ldquo;Fight for Freedom. Stand with Hong Kong.&rdquo; Facebook page持續更新。<br />\n<br />\n最後，民集團隊更會喺黎緊星期日1.12 舉辦《天下制裁集會》為1.19集定氣，打響頭炮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔥正牌攬炒Channel🔥<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/StirFryChannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStirFryChannel&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=6be85aa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/StirFryChannel</a><br />\n<br />\n#國際戰線 #本土戰線 #清算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5jxAQHO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jxAQHO.jpg&h=b8c68f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UpXUmPw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpXUmPw.jpg&h=8fa26607&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6884fbc703ff0bc204b781013c8a5f09abd5fcf2","tid":1822593,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:15:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53bfb1470b01cc8561a02bed4b47c17d1b8b86f5","tid":1822593,"uid":175731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3862aaeee88ef2b229dd8eb886c755ee7c2fa28","tid":1822593,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:22:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8b1e0c3fcee4f691f05203b51e29e342468b3c62","tid":1822593,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:22:59.000Z","msg":"借個位宣傳吸引火力黎推post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfor 想健康升級/心態體力提升手足參考<br />\n<br />\n入黎補補正能量調整心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人夠正能量先頂到落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自衞隊身體質素＆勇氣全世界都大有必要<br />\n香港人 only you can change yourself<br />\n未來嘅希望由我地做起<br />\n<br />\nStep 10.心存希望 管理情緒<br />\nHeal yourself🌱<br />\nFree yourself 🈵<br />\nFree the emotion🎉<br />\n無論咩時間 心存希望💛<br />\n我的使命係帶希望比大家<br />\n我地一齊行落去 <br />\n沒有處理不到的事<br />\n只有處理不到的心情<br />\n管理好情緒 有助我地做得更好<br />\n⚡️減少重複接觸影響自己的負面人事<br />\n🍎每日練習 突破舒適圈 比自己進步一下<br />\n🔥要增肌/提神/搵工心態/調理身體想心情更好歡迎黎搵我運動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：健康教練<br />\n啱嘅就聽下幫自己再幫人<br />\n 唔啱聽我都唔會覆你 <br />\n重點係大家Build up自信＋能耐做更強嘅自己 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">We can do it</span></span> <br />\n香港人團結 正能量<br />\n呢個世界唔係我地影響人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n我地要內在夠強 大返佢地<br />\n<br />\n永續健康身心 成功致勝<br />\n營養/心態歡迎搵我幫手<br />\n教完大家要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTG ME幫你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動打仗飲食法<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n支持升級黃圈 培訓人才人人出資資助小朋友就業<br />\n免費簡單健康分析<br />\n收費嘅跟進我都做 <br />\n支持黃圈返正價出錢幫人<br />\nNothing is free for granted <br />\nIf you Learn, do help more ppl<br />\n得閒係屋企/搵我做下運動放鬆<br />\nBuild up 自己自信 無狗敢搞你<br />\n如果你期望唔出付就會有結果<br />\n請你離開<br />\n<br />\nMy TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTreeHoIsGood&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=c95aae58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood</a><br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice\" data